Package: LDxBlocks
Type: Package
Title: LD Block Detection with Kinship-Adjusted Correlations (rV²) and Auto-Tuning
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Félicien", "Akohoue", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "akohoue.f@gmail.com"))
Description: Detect LD blocks using clique decomposition on kinship-adjusted LD (rV²),
    with an automatic parameter tuner minimizing unassigned GWAS markers.
